E-Commerce Website
A modern, responsive eCommerce website built using JavaScript and Bootstrap, following a design template from https://www.figma.com/design/DFYMKQPLYJVRBcuU9wS3E8/75%2B-Ecommerce-Landing-Page-Templates-(Community)?node-id=0-1&p=f&t=fjsFpGqkCqekkYNl-0.

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5, CSS3
Bootstrap 5 (for responsiveness and UI components)
JavaScript (for dynamic functionality)


🚀 Features
🛍️ Homepage with Featured Products
🔍 Search & Filtering Options
🛒 Shopping Cart with Add/Remove Items
💳 Checkout Page with Order Summary
📱 Fully Responsive Design
🌎 Multi-language & Currency Support (Planned)
